

=Bio=

Blogger and operator of netzpolitik.org (emphasises politics in digital society), co-founder of newthinking communications GmBH (agency for open source strategies), member of the German parliamentary committee of enquiry of ‘internet and digital society’, public relations and community building manager of the German Creative Commons, assistant lecturer at Mannheim University and the film academy in Ludwigsburg, co-organiser of the re:publica conference.


